        "TileImage": "$($repository 6f127239-2836-49cc-b97e-c11a01d5899b).Image",
        "Description": "Good Morning, 47. We have managed to get Intel on a group called &quot;The Lovebird Hunters&quot;. They are responsible for a mayor decline in couples, since they either use blackmail to make them break up, or even go as far as to assassinate them with either Belladonna or a hunting rifle as symbolism. We have located them to Dartmoor, where the Dartmoor Garden Show is taking place. Get up close and personal. Alternatively, go up to the balcony and hunt down the hunters from far away. Best of luck, 47.",
